Class EnquiryController

java.lang.Object
control.EnquiryController
All Implemented Interfaces:
EnquiryCreationController, EnquiryQueryController, EnquiryResponseController
public class EnquiryController extends Object implements EnquiryCreationController, EnquiryQueryController, EnquiryResponseController
The EnquiryController class manages the lifecycle of enquiries in the BTO Management System. This includes creation, modification, deletion, replying, and retrieval of enquiry data. Interfaces implemented: - EnquiryCreationController - EnquiryQueryController - EnquiryResponseController
